{"tid":565161,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"冬奧贏銅牌 俄羅斯冰壼運動員對禁藥呈陽性反應","createTime":"2018-02-18T17:11:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-10T02:59:54.000Z","uid":5195,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"f455c16d538a77a28894e0d43f7e45a923147284","tid":565161,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T17:11:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://sohanews.sohacdn.com/thumb_w/660/2018/2/18/photo1518959004851-1518959004852991346624.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsohanews.sohacdn.com%2Fthumb_w%2F660%2F2018%2F2%2F18%2Fphoto1518959004851-1518959004852991346624.png&h=7f2d2dfe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯傳媒報道，剛在平昌冬奧會贏得冰壺混雙銅牌的俄羅斯男選手克魯舍爾尼茨基，懷疑被驗出服用禁藥米屈肼。俄羅斯奧林匹克運動員發言人說，代表團收到國際奧委會的通知，指一名俄國運動員可能驗出服用禁藥，目前正等候第二個樣本的化驗結果。<br />\n<br />\n國際奧委會去年底以俄羅斯在索契冬奧會期間大規模使用禁藥為由，禁止俄羅斯代表團參加平昌冬奧會，但邀請一百六十八名符合條件的俄國運動員以個人名義參賽。米屈肼是用於治療心臟病的藥物，在俄羅斯和東歐國家廣泛使用，一六年被世界反興奮劑機構首次納入違禁藥品名單，俄羅斯網球明星舒拉寶娃當年檢測出米屈肼呈陽性反應，被禁賽十五個月。"},{"pid":"a5986edc82b77c3c27316de095aed29b3a0d4dd5","tid":565161,"uid":125814,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T17:16:37.000Z","msg":"上屆出左事 今屆又黎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcbd26ee4032bd3cfb37a38ab62c2fc317d2d94e","tid":565161,"uid":165978,"like":65,"dislike":1,"score":64,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T17:18:23.000Z","msg":"屌你冰壺呢啲咁技術性嘅野都食禁藥<img src=\"/as